data.description:
Introducing a stunning two-story residence that offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home boasts a spacious 3-car garage and is located in a highly desirable neighborhood, just 1 mile away from the vibrant downtown Chandler nightlife and dining scene, making it the epitome of modern suburban living.
Key Features:
Interior:
* Bedrooms: This home features four generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for both family and guests. Each bedroom offers comfort and privacy, making it ideal for a growing family or those who love to entertain.
* Bathrooms: With 2.5 beautifully appointed bathrooms, including a master ensuite, you'll have all the space you need to pamper yourself and unwind after a long day. * Great Room: The open and inviting great room is the heart of this home, where you can relax or entertain guests in style. Its spacious layout and abundant natural light create an inviting atmosphere.
* Loft: Upstairs, you'll find a versatile loft space that can be used as a playroom, home office, or a second entertainment area. Its flexibility allows you to tailor it to your specific needs.
* Formal Dining: The formal dining area is perfect for hosting elegant dinners and special occasions, providing a refined space for memorable gatherings.
* Built-In Office Area: For those who work from home, a built-in office area offers a dedicated space to focus and be productive while enjoying the comfort of your own home.
* Recently Complete Interior Paint: The interior of the home has been thoughtfully updated with fresh paint, providing a clean and modern aesthetic.
EXTERIOR:
* Covered Patio: Step outside to the covered patio and experience the joys of outdoor living. Whether you're sipping morning coffee or hosting a BBQ, this space offers a comfortable retreat.
* Garage: The spacious 3-car garage not only provides ample parking but also offers additional storage space for all your belongings.
LOCATION: 
*Proximity to Downtown Chandler: Situated just 1 mile away from vibrant downtown Chandler, you'll have easy access to a plethora of restaurants, cafes, boutiques, and entertainment options. Enjoy the lively atmosphere and explore the local culture.
* Convenient Access to 202 Freeway: Being only 2 miles from the 202 freeway, commuting to work or exploring the greater Phoenix area is a breeze.
This meticulously maintained home is a true gem, offering an ideal blend of modern amenities, space, and a prime location close to all that Chandler has to offer. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home. Come see it and experience the best of suburban living!
